
Options
    -m <mod>    module name
    -i <fn>     hosts file
    -a          args for module
    -l <host>   limit to one host
    
    -vv     verbose
    -vvv    extra verbose for ssh issues

    --check check playbook syntax

Modules
    copy    copy file from local to remote
            args: src=<path dest=<path>

    setup   gather info 
            args: filter=<key>



    dnf     Fedora
            args: dnf: name=httpd state=latest
